    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>**Dreams of Sand is still in development - footage, screenshots etc. are not necessarily representative of the final version of the game.**</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reverie: Dreams of Sand is a story-rich Sokoban-like time-manipulation puzzle game. You play as Reverie, a scientist struggling to formulate a cure for their lifelong disease, dreaming about their past, present and future. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate and solve 50+ puzzles by pushing blocks, manipulating time and navigating small grid-based spaces in dreamy desert environments based on various locations from Reverie’s life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/03c92863fb5b2e7a82f45e67d4c29011.poster.avif?t=1746935607\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/03c92863fb5b2e7a82f45e67d4c29011.webm?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/03c92863fb5b2e7a82f45e67d4c29011.mp4?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the memories of a person's life from childhood to present day. Decide how they remember the events from their past, affecting who they are in the present and who they may become long into the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tightly designed Grid-Based Puzzles</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/ac5274417afbf08a969a72ff11aaccbb.poster.avif?t=1746935607\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/ac5274417afbf08a969a72ff11aaccbb.webm?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/ac5274417afbf08a969a72ff11aaccbb.mp4?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vibrant 3D Visuals</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/263b7efe49ffdb950a94c924250183d7.poster.avif?t=1746935607\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/263b7efe49ffdb950a94c924250183d7.webm?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/263b7efe49ffdb950a94c924250183d7.mp4?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short-Story with Branching Choices</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/74a64e90e5f3072c9e23fcabcb41b711.poster.avif?t=1746935607\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/74a64e90e5f3072c9e23fcabcb41b711.webm?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/74a64e90e5f3072c9e23fcabcb41b711.mp4?t=1746935607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
